{"tid":1641953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天琦：書面裁決將於四星期內頒布","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:19.000Z","uid":68738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"675093dffa54db6d93b94993050a59b3da838b9a","tid":1641953,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"感謝各位市民到高等法院聲援，特別是通宵達旦等候，或天未光便出門的朋友。遺憾庭內座位有限，未能讓所有人進入近睹天琦，但你們的心意想必已順利傳達給他。<br />\n<br />\n法官今日已聽取控方及上訴方陳詞，預計將於四星期內頒布書面裁決。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，大家也可繼續寫信支持天琦。寄信注意事項請閱：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/VTRvqK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVTRvqK&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=3b1c6f93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/VTRvqK</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wtp6qWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtp6qWg.jpg&h=5c36a887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei/photos/a.172255923187252/756135468132625?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleungtinkei%2Fphotos%2Fa.172255923187252%2F756135468132625%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=8695d669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei/photos/a.172255923187252/756135468132625?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df30326113bbed5168cffb0f5a3fda6f7ff9226","tid":1641953,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"另類連儂牆 家家戶戶都知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}